Rohini College of Engineering & Technology (RCET) aims to be a center of educational excellence in rural areas, providing cutting-edge technical education to nurture competent, ethical engineers who serve the nation and society. Its mission focuses on fostering technically skilled graduates through quality education, research, and disseminating knowledge in key areas like science, agriculture, and industry, promoting research-assisted learning for societal benefit. 
Vision
To be a leading academic institution offering continuous excellence in education and research, particularly in rural settings, serving the nation by nurturing highly competent, ethical, and socially responsible engineering graduates. 
Mission
To cultivate technically competent graduates by delivering state-of-the-art engineering education.
To promote research-driven scientific learning through knowledge dissemination in science, agriculture, industry, and national security.
To foster a conducive environment for interpersonal bonding, aesthetic sense, and global harmony.
To support high-quality, translational research and deep connections with industry and community. 
